              },
              "free_text": [
                " At 15-170 MeV."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "SYNCY"
                ],
                "institute": "2ZZZCER"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " At 160-570 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The targets were uranium foils, delivered as high",
                "purity material. Three different foils of thickness",
                "2.54 mm, 0.127 mm and 0.0254 mm, respectively, were",
                "used during the course of the experiments.",
                "Before irradiation, the uranium foils were cleaned with",
                " approx. 6m HNO(3) for a few minutes to remove the",
                "oxide layer, washed with ethanol and dried.",
                "The Uppsala irradiations were performed with the",
                "uranium foil of thickness approx. 2.54 mm, the CERN",
                "with foils of thicknesses 0.127 mm and 0.0254 mm.",
                "table 2 of the paper contains results of analysis of",
                "different uranium foils for contaminations."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "INTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The duration of the internal irradiations was in",
                "Uppsala 4 hr and the beam intensity 0.25-0.45 uA,",
                "at CERN 1 hr and 0.84-1.00 uA."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " At 600 MeV the activities of Na-24 and Mg-28",
                "were measured by direct gamma-counting of the",
                "irradiated target, using the fission product I-135 as",
                "internal monitor and/or using separate aluminium",
                "monitor foils."
              ]
            }
          ],
