          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The over-all uncertainty in the measured",
                "cross sections, including the counting statistics and",
                "errors in detector efficiency, chemical yield",
                "determination, branching ratio and contribution from",
                "impurities is estimated to about 10% for Mg-28 and",
                "about 10-20% for Na-24.",
                "However, the cross section values for Na-24 for",
                "energies of less than 160 MeV will have a greater",
                " uncertainty, due to the large discrepancies in the",
                "determination of the impurities in the targets used",
                "in these experiments."
              ]
            }
